Robert Bray https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Robert_Bray 0 Robert E. Bray (October 23, 1917 – March 7, 1983) was an American film and television actor probably best remembered for his role as the forest ranger Corey Stuart in the CBS series Lassie. He also starred in The Lone Ranger and Stagecoach West.
